- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is the most likely category as the paper deals with automata and regular languages. 
- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is also likely as the paper involves combinatorial and graph theoretic concepts. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is relevant as the paper involves proving lower bounds and characterizing regular languages. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) may be relevant as the paper involves analyzing the complexity of synchronizing automata. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) may be relevant as the paper involves studying the behavior of automata.
